<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Giriş Yap</title>
    <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body class="bg-light">
    <div class="container d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center vh-100">
        <div class="card p-4 shadow-lg" style="width: 100%; max-width: 400px;">
            <h2 class="text-center mb-4">Giriş Yap</h2>
            <% if (error) { %>
                <div class="alert alert-danger" role="alert">
                    <%= error %>
                </div>
            <% } %>
            <form action="/login" method="POST">
                <div class="mb-3">
                    <label for="username" class="form-label">Kullanıcı Adı</label>
                    <input type="text" name="username" id="username" class="form-control" placeholder="Kullanıcı Adı" required>
                </div>
                <div class="mb-3">
                    <label for="password" class="form-label">Şifre</label>
                    <input type="password" name="password" id="password" class="form-control" placeholder="Şifre" required>
                </div>
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary w-100">Giriş Yap</button>
            </form>
            <p class="text-center mt-3">
                Henüz bir hesabınız yok mu? <a href="/register">Kayıt Ol</a>
            </p>
            <hr>
            <!-- Açıklama Metni -->
            <div class="text-center text-muted mt-3" style="font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.6;">
                <p><strong>HOŞGELDİNİZ.</strong></p>
                <p>BU SİTE STOK DEPOLAMA VE TAKİBİ İÇİN KULLANILMAKTADIR VE ÜCRETSİZ OLARAK SUNULMAKTADIR.</p>
                <p><strong>TÜM HAKLARI SAKLIDIR.</strong></p>
                <p>Yunus Emre USLU tarafından oluşturulmuştur.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <!-- Bootstrap JS -->
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>